<h1>Overview</h1>
<hr>
<p>As times go, the original allocation percentages among assets change because of asset appreciation or depreciation. Techniques are needed to rebalance the allocation back to target allocation percentages are called rebalancing strategies. A good rebalancing strategy could help improve the portfolio return (ranging from 0.1% to 1 or 2%) while reducing portfolio volatility.</p>
<p>ValidFi collects both periodical (such as annual) rebalancing and opportunistic rebalancing strategies.  </p>
